    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated S65 platform. The 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,400 RPM redline, is mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically impeccable; the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with VAC-coated shells and ARP hardware. The chassis is free of subframe fatigue, and the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) valves operate with factory-spec response. The exterior maintains its original paint depth across all panels, and the carbon fiber roof's clear coat is free of UV degradation. A turn-key, collector-grade vehicle with a comprehensive service dossier and consistent oil analysis results.",
