      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle. Meticulously maintained and garage-kept under a soft cover, the exterior retains its original factory luster with laser-straight body lines and zero road rash. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather is supple with no creasing, the carpets are spotless, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive folder of service records and a recent multi-point inspection confirming zero leaks or mechanical wear. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched factory tool kit, this vehicle is a collector-grade example that must be seen in person to be fully appreciated. Clean title in hand.",
